  "name": "Forgotten Presence",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/light-royal-1.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per day as an immediate action, you can cause a creature to forget that you were present for the last minute per oracle level, including forgetting all actions you took during that time, unless it succeeds at a Will save (DC 10 + 1/2 your oracle level + your Charisma modifier). Effects such as&nbsp;modify memory&nbsp;can restore the lost memories.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, you can use this ability twice per day.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>"
